Valdez, Paul [Allan Geoffrey Yates]

Feline Frame-Up

Transport Publishing Co, 1952. First Edition. Unknown. 8vo - over 7他" - 9他" Near Fine / No Jacket. Item #005490762

32pp., including color cover. Part of the Scientific Thriller series. A very nice copy, with little to no wear; usual rusting to the staples. Valdez was the pseudonym for noted Australlian crime writter Allan Geoffrey Yates (1923-1985) A story of the mob, a murder, and frame-up. 'Mark ran the town for himself--he could knock off the other mobsters easily--but wasn't he signing his own death warrant when he let a woman plan the...'.
